lount\" /><ref>{{cite web|title=Walbridge, Russell D. office record|work=state archives digital collections|publisher=state of Hawaii|url=https://digitalcollections.hawaii.gov/greenstone3/sites/localsite/collect/governm1/index/assoc/HASH0139/73fcf24f.dir/doc.pdf|accessdate=February 3, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220111623/https://digitalcollections.hawaii.gov/greenstone3/sites/localsite/collect/governm1/index/assoc/HASH0139/73fcf24f.dir/doc.pdf|archive-date=February 20, 2017|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{sortname|Charles Otto|Berger}}\n|[[Oahu]]\n|National Reform\n|National Reform\n|\n|<ref name=\"Lydecker\" /><ref name=\"Election\" /><ref name=\"Blount\" /><ref>{{cite web|title=Berger, Charles Otto office record|work=state archives digital collections|publisher=state of Hawaii|url=https://digitalcollections.hawaii.gov/greenstone3/sites/localsite/collect/governm1/index/assoc/HASH01a1/8eb58e73.dir/doc.pdf|accessdate=February 3, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220100432/https://digitalcollections.hawaii.gov/greenstone3/sites/localsite/collect/governm1/index/assoc/HASH01a1/8eb58e73.dir/doc.pdf|archive-date=February 20, 2017|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{sortname|John Adams|Cummins}}\n|[[Oahu]]\n|National Reform\n|National Reform\n|\n|<ref name=\"Lydecker\" /><ref name=\"Election\" /><ref name=\"Blount\" /><ref>{{cite web|title=Cummins, John A. office record|work=state archives digital collections|publisher=state of Hawaii|url=https://digitalcollections.hawaii.gov/greenstone3/sites/localsite/collect/governm1/index/assoc/HASH0652.dir/doc.pdf|accessdate=February 3, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220095455/https://digitalcollections.hawaii.gov/greenstone3/sites/localsite/collect/governm1/index/assoc/HASH0652.dir/doc.pdf|archive-date=February 20, 2017|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{sortname|John|Ena|John Ena Jr.}}\n|[[Oahu]]\n|National Reform\n|National Reform\n|\n|<ref name=\"L